divs: sighting detailsit was afternoon, the sky was quite clear, not too much cloud. i was sitting in a moving sedan next to my friend who was driving. the car was moving about 30mile\hr , quite stable velocity, minimum acceleration in the great highway, next to the pacific ocean. as the car moving to the south, looking to the right side of the window, there were two cigar-shaped object flying side by side in a calmly fashion as long as my observation lasted about 5 minutes. the distance of them from our moving car was quite far, but was clear enough. i was staring at them until they are out of sight from the passanger seat window next to the driver seat.
